<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.1">
<l>naṇṇātār muṟuvalippa nalluṟṟār karaintēṅka</l>
<l>veṇṇārāt tuyarviḷaikku mivaiyeṉṉa vulakiyaṟkai</l>
<l>kaṇṇāḷā kaṭalkaṭaintā yuṉakaḻaṟkē varumparicu</l>
<l>taṇṇāvā taṭiyēṉaip paṇikaṇṭāy cāmāṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While those who are not close [to me] smile, while those who feel well[-disposed towards me] cry [and] lament,</l>
<l>what are these that ripen afflictions the count of which does not become full? The nature of the world,</l>
<l>o husband, you who churned the ocean. Without delay bestow on me your servant</l>
<l>a way that leads to your ankleted [feet], see, [or] a way to die.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
